emuInput.TitMainTitle: Lot with Dumpster, debris, and garbage, at intersection of Crawford, Pride, Reed, and Colwell streets, with Civic Arena construction in background, Hill District
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 14, 1960, pg. 2 reads: " 'Rubbish Island' - This "Rubbish Island" at the Crawford, Pride, Reed and Colwell intersection has been growing for quite some time without being disturbed by the city clean-up squads."
